@host = http://localhost:5068
@apiKey = dev-local-key-9R4mT8Xk

### Create a shipment (POST → 201 Created)
POST {{host}}/api/shipments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "senderName": "Ahmet Yılmaz",
  "receiverName": "Fatma Kaya",
  "origin": "Istanbul",
  "destination": "Ankara"
}

###

### List all shipments (GET → 200 OK)
GET {{host}}/api/shipments
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Update status — replace TR20260622-XXXXXX with the tracking number from the POST response
PUT {{host}}/api/shipments/TR20260623-7MZZR5/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "newStatus": "InTransit",
  "note": "Cleared for customs inspection"
}

###

### Public tracking lookup — no API key required (anonymous)
### Replace TR20260623-7MZZR5 with the tracking number from the POST response above
GET {{host}}/api/track/TR20260623-7MZZR5
